                  <h3 class="card-title">Messaging locked in before design starts</h3>
                  <p>Figma stays closed until we nail the strategy. We define your positioning, content hierarchy, and user flows first, so every element on the site solves an actual client problem, not just looks good.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-element">
                  <h3 class="card-title"><strong>A site that looks like it costs what you charge</strong></h3>
                  <p>Design that mirrors your expertise and pricing. Clean, confident, and free of visual noise, so clients instantly perceive competence and reliability without having to guess.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-element">
                  <h3 class="card-title">Professional websites you can easily keep up to date</h3>
                  <p>I deliver fully SEO-optimized, high-performance sites with clean structure and a CMS, so your team can update services, cases, and content anytime. No need to call me for every little change.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-element">
                  <h3 class="card-title">Feedback without the drama</h3>
                  <p>You see work in stages, not in one big “ta‑da”. We refine as we go, with clear rounds of feedback, so the project doesn’t turn into a revision nightmare.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-element">
                  <h3 class="card-title">Launch and what’s after</h3>
                  <p>I don&#x27;t vanish after launch. You get 30 days of free post-launch support: bug fixes, performance tweaks, and video walkthroughs so you can confidently update content without me.</p>
