                    <p>Websites are closers, not prospectors. They turn &quot;maybe&quot; into &quot;yes&quot; when someone visits. Website doesn&#x27;t hunt down clients while you sleep. It amplify what you&#x27;re already doing: marketing, networking, referrals. Expect better conversion from existing traffic, not traffic from thin air.</p>
